@startuml
title UC08 — Student practices pronunciation — Sequence
actor "Student" as Actor
participant "PronunciationPage" as UI
participant "API Gateway" as API
participant "PronunciationService" as PronunciationService
database "MySQL" as DB
participant "ElevenLabs API" as ElevenLabs_API
Actor -> UI : start pronunciation attempt
UI -> API : HTTPS request
API -> PronunciationService : route and authorize
PronunciationService -> DB : read/write PronunciationAttempt
DB -->> PronunciationService : data result
PronunciationService -> ElevenLabs_API : integration request
ElevenLabs_API -->> PronunciationService : integration response
PronunciationService -->> API : response
API -->> UI : JSON result
UI -->> Actor : score and feedback are displayed
@enduml
